	        Send us your pictures   ·  Send us your stories FOUR boys from Hambanathi Township will represent South Africa in Japan at the Karate World Championships to be held next month. Lwandile Msane, Mbulelo Ndlovu, Mesuli Ngubane and Nduduzo Sekoati are all pupils at Mbonisweni Primary School. 24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.  